 | 2026-04-25 | GameLoop.step no longer auto-advances | World.runTick now calls gameLoop.advance() directly so the gameLoop tick aligns with the diff tick when listeners fire. GameLoop is internal-only (not in src/index.ts). |
+| 2026-04-25 | findNearest correctness + snapshot isolation (v0.4.1) | findNearest maxRadius now `ceil(hypot(W-1,H-1))` so diagonal-corner entities are reachable; serialize/deserialize structuredClone component data and state values to isolate snapshots from live engine state. |
+| 2026-04-25 | Removed in-place mutation auto-detection (v0.5.0, breaking) | `ComponentStoreOptions.detectInPlaceMutations`, `WorldConfig.detectInPlacePositionMutations`, `World.markPositionDirty`, the per-tick spatial sync scan, and `WorldMetrics.spatial.fullScans`/`scannedEntities`/`durationMs.spatialSync` all removed. All mutations must go through `setComponent`/`setPosition`. `world.grid` is now a runtime-immutable read-only delegate. `EventBus.emit` rejects non-JSON payloads. |
